    "TRAN_2": "Motivation to Join: Organizations join Alliances for many reasons. The following questions are focused on understanding what motivated your organization to join the Salem Youth Sports Alliance.\n\n \n\nPlease rate your agreement with the following statements.\n\n \n\nMy organization joined the Salem Youth Sports  Alliance to... - Address complex social problems that one organization cannot solve on its own",
    "TRAN_3": "Motivation to Join: Organizations join Alliances for many reasons. The following questions are focused on understanding what motivated your organization to join the Salem Youth Sports Alliance.\n\n \n\nPlease rate your agreement with the following statements.\n\n \n\nMy organization joined the Salem Youth Sports  Alliance to... - Create a system for change or system of program delivery where none existed before",
