    "GC_2": "Goal Consensus: Goal consensus relates to the degree to which organizations agree on network-level goals. The following questions are focused on understanding the degree of goal consensus among organizations involved in the Salem Youth Sports Alliance.\n\n\n\nPlease rate your agreement with the following statements. - Member organizations agree upon the overall goals and objectives of the Salem Youth Sports  Alliance",
    "GC_3": "Goal Consensus: Goal consensus relates to the degree to which organizations agree on network-level goals. The following questions are focused on understanding the degree of goal consensus among organizations involved in the Salem Youth Sports Alliance.\n\n\n\nPlease rate your agreement with the following statements. - There is clarity on the vision for where the Salem Youth Sports  Alliance should be going",
