    "COM_2": "Communication: Communication relates to the quality of interactions between organizations in the Salem Youth Sports Alliance. The following questions are focused on the level of continuous communication associated with the Salem Youth Sports Alliance.\n\n\n\nPlease rate your agreement with the following statements. - The Salem Youth Sports  Alliance provides a safe environment in which disagreements and conflicts can be discussed",
