    "COH_2": "Cohesion: Cohesion relates to the sense of unity and togetherness among organizations involved in the Salem Youth Sports Alliance. The following questions are focused on the level of cohesion associated with the Salem Youth Sports Alliance.\n\n\n\nPlease rate your agreement with the following statements. - There is a strong feeling of belonging in the Salem Youth Sports  Alliance",
    "COH_3": "Cohesion: Cohesion relates to the sense of unity and togetherness among organizations involved in the Salem Youth Sports Alliance. The following questions are focused on the level of cohesion associated with the Salem Youth Sports Alliance.\n\n\n\nPlease rate your agreement with the following statements. - My organization is proud to be a part of the Salem Youth Sports  Alliance",
